         <ab>VVrS88.5 Var. a (mss. 4000, 4010, 4020, 4025, 4040, 4050, 4161, 4162):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            barsom az māhrōy stānišn <em>mat̰ vā̊</em> gām-ē abar kunišn padāiš yā gām-ē abar kunišn <em>frasrūtā īžaiiā̊</em> gām-ē abar kunišn</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "He has to take the <em>barsom</em> from the <em>māhrōy</em>. At <em>mat̰ vā̊</em>, he has to advance one step. At <em>padāiš yā</em>, he has to advance one step.
            At <em>frasrūtā īžaiiā̊</em>, he has to advance one step."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
   </Ritual>
